Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.96,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,You Only Live Once
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:13.64,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,You're so beautiful Tonight 見とれていたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:17.52,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,砂時計さえ止まる Take my breath away
